# Trace regression catalog
#
# Smoke traces collected from peer-crate smoke runs are stored here
# as JSON files.  CI replays every trace against a fresh harness to
# catch behavioural regressions.
#
# Format: one file per peer crate per milestone, e.g.:
#   dir_index_v1.0.json
#   extent_map_v1.0.json
#   object_store_v1.0.json
